snippet.title: Project Kat - An unconventional horror RPG
snippet.description:
Free on itch.io https://leef6010.itch.io/projectkat There's something spooky happening at your school, and it might be all your fault. Check out this puzzling horror adventure with multiple ways to progress through all of its spooky challenges.
